"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-simone-biles-shakes-off-injury-shines-us-dominant-paris-debut\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Three years almost to the day later, there Simone Biles was again, alone on the floor of an Olympic arena, her thoughts her own, as the world wondered if she would continue competing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 29}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic arena\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 105}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as she did in Tokyo, Biles huddled with U.S. gymnastics team doctor Marcia Faustin.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999774119482943, \"rank\": 2.258236267585922e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcia_Overstrand\", \"score\": 0.999998407546531, \"rank\": 1.5917846918190336e-06, \"text\": \"Marcia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcia_Overstrand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcia_Overstrand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as she did in Tokyo, Biles briefly disappeared into a back hallway.\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999774119482943, \"rank\": 2.258236267585922e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"a back hallway\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as she did in Tokyo, Biles gave viewers reason to hold their breath.\\u00c2 But Biles is in Paris, and she seems to have left the twisties\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the vertigo that sidelined her last time\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094behind.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999774119482943, \"rank\": 2.258236267585922e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0516381494388613e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"reason\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"their breath\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the vertigo\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"her last time\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094behind\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time she returned to the floor, limping a bit on her newly taped left calf, and produced simply an astonishing performance to take the lead in nearly every category in the qualifying session on Sunday.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIncredible,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said U.S. technical lead Chellsie Memmel.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chellsie_Memmel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chellsie Memmel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chellsie_Memmel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chellsie_Memmel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"her newly taped left calf\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"simply an astonishing performance\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly every category\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying session\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After it was over and she had sealed the U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s spot in the team final\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and all but sealed her own in three event finals\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Biles bounded to the edge of the uneven bars podium, took a bow, waved and blew a kiss to the crowd.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s spot\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"three event finals\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Biles\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the edge\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars podium\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"a bow\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"a kiss\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 59.566 was the second best score of the Olympic cycle among gymnasts in the field, second only to her own all-around in the first session of this spring\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national championships, when she produced a 60.45.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"the second best score\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic cycle\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"her own all-around\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the first session\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"national championships\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She holds the other eight of the top 10, too.)\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even on one foot, Biles is the best of all time.\\u00c2 With three of five subdivisions still due to compete on Sunday, as of this writing, the Americans left themselves in good position: first overall in the team competition, for which they have guaranteed a spot; first for Biles and second for reigning Olympic champion Sunisa Lee in the all-around; first for Biles and second for Jade Carey in the vault; third for Sunisa Lee in the uneven bars; second for Biles and third for Lee in the balance beam; and first for Biles and second for Jordan Chiles in the floor exercise.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 1681, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \