dbpedia.org/resource/Russians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Landi\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s performance\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cpretty amazing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cnot\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"The energy\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"a full point\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"mistakes\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"every gymnast\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Russians are not here this time, a punishment for their country\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s war in Ukraine, and this time, when the Americans made errors, they rebounded.\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2825, \"end\": 2833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russians\", \"score\": 0.9987893259217322, \"rank\": 0.001212060538828142, \"text\": \"Russians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russians\"}, {\"begin\": 2900, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9959105296265807, \"rank\": 0.004093692105935264, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their country\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s war\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"errors\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Memmel acknowledged some visible nervousness from 16-year-old Hezly Rivera on the balance beam, which opened the day, but she then performed well on the uneven bars.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Memmel\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"some visible nervousness\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"16-year-old Hezly Rivera\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3089}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carey, the reigning Olympic floor exercise champion, went out of bounds twice on the apparatus and then bailed out of her last pass to miss the final, but she gathered herself and hit her vault.\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0499365158027606e-23, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reigning Olympic floor exercise champion\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"bounds\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"the apparatus\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"her last pass\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"her vault\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles made a few missteps, mostly on account of her overwhelming power, but she seemed in control of her emotions.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 \\u00c2 And at first, it was her mental state that offered the most questions.\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"a few missteps\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3359}, {\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\"